Title: Hypertension secondary to an adrenal pseudocyst cured by laparoscopic partial adrenalectomy.
Abstract: Resection of a large adrenal cyst does not necessarily imply total adrenalectomy. We depict transperitoneal laparoscopic partial adrenalectomy of a pseudocyst in a hypertensive adult.
