Title: Vesicular prurigo pigmentosa cured by minocycline.
Abstract: We present 1 case of prurigo pigmentosa associated with vesicles that we call 'vesicular prurigo pigmentosa'. The subject was treated using minocycline with good results and no recurrence of the lesions over a 2-year period.
